node.text:
An exciting #UCL start for @fcbayern tomorrow. #FCBayern is still in the process of implementing the ideas of coach @julian.nagelsmann and @fcbarcelona has lost a lot of quality with the departures of @leomessi and @antogriezmann. I am very much looking forward to the game. 💪🏼

Since the @championsleague finally starts again, I'll do a Q&A on TWITTER. Send me your #UCL questions using #AskBasti and I will answer some of them. I'm looking forward to it!

node.text: Finally, it's game day again in the @NFL! I wish the @ChicagoBears good luck in their season opener on #SundayNightFootball against the @Rams. This team looks very promising and I am excited to see what they can accomplish this year. Bear down! 🐻⬇️
